name: Nothing But Us Official Website
body:
### Who we are
We are a group of people who want the world a better place. We make entreteriment, information, and funny videos. Our group is composed of three people. Diogo, Matheus, and Samuel. I am responsible for the information, technologgy, and moderation parts. I find the programs we are going to use for our videos. I make information videos. I also moderate the channel, reporting inapropriate content. Matheus is resposnible for the entreteriment part. He makes wonderful game play videos. Samuel is responsible for the planning and entreteriment part. He plans how the video will be. He also makes great game play videos.

### Programs we use
We use many programs to make our videos. We use many programs so that we can have the best quality videos. Some programs we use are: [Powtoon](www.powtoon.com), [Quicktime](https://support.apple.com/downloads/quicktime), [Ezid](www.ezvid.com), and [Camstudio](camstudio.org). Pontoon we use for informative videos. We use QuickTime for screen recording and video editing on Mac. We use Ezvid for screen recording and video editing on Windows. We use CamStudio for screen recording.

### Visit our profiles
Each of the members of the channel have a profile. For you to see a person’s profile visit nothing-but-us.github.io/member's_name. To see Matheus’ profile visit nothineeg-but-us.github.io/matheus. To see Diogo’s profile visit nothing-but-us.github.io/diogo. To see Samuel’s profile visit nothing-but-us.github.io/samuel. At the profile you can see basic information about the member such as email and name.

### Nothing But Us on Social Media
You can visit us at Youtube /NothingButUs, Instagram @nothing.but.us.official, and github @nothing-but-us. Unfortunately we don’t have Facebook and Twitter. Any accounts under NothingButUs at Facebook and Twitter are unofficial. Please subscribe to our channel! Follow us at Instagram and Twitter.

### Contact Us
Comments and Suggestions? Contact us at nothing.but.us@gmail.com. You can also contact us by commenting at our channel page. If you send us a email it might take 3 to 4 week days for us to reply.
